PARLIAMENT OF KENYA

Following an adoption of the Report of the Procedure and House Rules Committee that amended Standing Order 25A to allow Cabinet Secretaries to physically appear before the House and answer questions;

Today, I appeared before Parliament and expounded on Government policy, replied to questions and provided reports concerning matters under the Ministry of Water, Sanitation and Irrigation.
